{"tid":1834693,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子已到","createTime":"2020-01-22T13:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T22:17:37.000Z","uid":66146,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0affcc2be792d300327b6d213c59cb2c70fcd3f3","tid":1834693,"uid":66146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:41:07.000Z","msg":"2012又好,927又好,UFO又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg&h=fc554873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dHRiV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dHRiV5.jpg&h=bb698acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg&h=61f1bb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2289bd3b5d4b2f5b61d4c4c2f76857ad39c97daf","tid":1834693,"uid":351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:42:47.000Z","msg":"咁唔係午餐肉嘅話有無西屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f164077f475e6b60c3a2f4d8be0caa238a576d2d","tid":1834693,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"手持口罩就可以有西屌的日子已到"},{"pid":"8d731b281fd29e05949e64e304c83437aa51a73d","tid":1834693,"uid":174692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"驚你未等到有西屌 已經病死咗嘅毒撚"},{"pid":"23fc5a9396a173c0313bcda3f09f31fe06b41b65","tid":1834693,"uid":120206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"牛餐肉過曬期未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a526aa6c3145f23388eb6eee1c7b061c3683a4","tid":1834693,"uid":66146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"23fc5a9396a173c0313bcda3f09f31fe06b41b65","tid":1834693,"uid":120206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"牛餐肉過曬期未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:57:46.000Z","msg":"已經重新入貨"},{"pid":"70b7a38f70f2ffa3abdf54442200d4840ce38525","tid":1834693,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"我揾到櫃底有罐紅肚兜<br />\n有冇絲想用閪換"},{"pid":"676098deb74b9adf8a8bd25b0a0fb84c364fd076","tid":1834693,"uid":5725,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"口罩都冇想屌西"},{"pid":"33bd74dd4694cd2b57a68bebb3040998750cb632","tid":1834693,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:59:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f4fb2a286a2c8a2d597da8667896508106d7a2af","tid":1834